Steps to create the k8s cluster:
(I have created the cluster using Kind)
1. Install docker
2. Install go and setup it's path
3. Install kind:
   curl -Lo ./kind "https://kind.sigs.k8s.io/dl/v0.7.0/kind-$(uname)-amd64"
   chmod +x ./kind
   mv ./kind /usr/bin/kind
4. Create the cluster
   kind create cluster

Links referred:
1) https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/kind